OL,3,CAdnan Sarwar reports on an assessment
OL,4,Cof the UK's defence strategy
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Keir Starmer confirmed
OL,7,Fgovernment plans to sharply increase
OL,8,Fdefence spending, in what he said was
OL,9,Fthe biggest increase in defence
OL,10,Fspending, since the end of The Cold
OL,11,FWar. The announcement came just days
OL,12,Fafter he said British troops may be
OL,13,Fsent to Ukraine as part of a
OL,14,Fpeacekeeping force. As Donald Trump
OL,15,Fplans negotiations with Vladimir
OL,16,FPutin, Ukraine's President Zelensky
OL,17,Fhas called for an army of Europe to be
OL,18,Fassembled. In this volatile
OL,19,Finternational climate, how well
OL,20,Fprepared are our armed forces for any
OL,21,Ffuture conflict?
