OL,3,CAdnan Sarwar reports on an assessment
OL,4,Cof the UK's defence strategy
OL,6,FIn this week's episode of the Tonight
OL,7,Fprogramme, former British soldier
OL,8,FAdnan Sarwar investigates the UK's
OL,9,Fdefence strategy; asking whether
OL,10,Fcurrent levels of equipment and
OL,11,Fmanpower are adequate, and whether the
OL,12,Fright level of funding is in place to
OL,13,Fmeet the challenges of the future.
