OL,3,CAdnan Sarwar reports on an assessment
OL,4,Cof the UK's defence strategy
OL,6,FBut what could a future war look like?
OL,7,FAdnan meets ex-British soldier Stephen
OL,8,Fwho hadn't served for nine years until
OL,9,Fhe made the decision in 2022 to travel
OL,10,Fto Ukraine to fight. Stephen recounts
OL,11,Fhow fighting on the frontline has
OL,12,Fchanged from his time in Afghanistan,
OL,13,Fincluding a first-hand encounter with
OL,14,Fdrone warfare.
