OL,3,CAdnan Sarwar reports on an assessment
OL,4,Cof the UK's defence strategy
OL,6,FWhilst the development of AI and drone
OL,7,Fwarfare is expected to play an
OL,8,Fincreasingly important role in
OL,9,Fconflicts of the future, military
OL,10,Ffigures around the UK are sounding the
OL,11,Falarm that Britain is dangerously
OL,12,Funder-defended right now.
