OL,3,CAdnan Sarwar reports on an assessment
OL,4,Cof the UK's defence strategy
OL,6,FMinistry of Defence figures show that
OL,7,Fthe size of the British army is at its
OL,8,Fsmallest since the Napoleonic era, and
OL,9,Falthough the UK has been spending more
OL,10,Fon defence in recent years, it has had
OL,11,Fone of the slowest rates of spending
OL,12,Fincreases out of all Nato countries.
OL,13,FThe UK now faces stark choices about
OL,14,Fits defence, but whether government
OL,15,Fplans will meet the increasing
OL,16,Fchallenges Britain now faces remains
OL,17,Fto be seen.
OL,19,FWatch War: Would Britain Be Ready?
OL,20,FTonight, on ITV1 at 8:30pm
